sentence: The tech-heavy Nasdaq was set to open slightly higher on Wednesday after upbeat business updates from Salesforce and HP Enterprise, while the S&P 500 headed for a subdued start.

.N

At 8.30 a.m.ET, Dow e-minis 1YMc1 were down 0.15% at 28,152.
S&P 500 e-minis ESc1 were up 0.04% at 3,444.5, while Nasdaq 100 e-minis NQc1 were up 0.20% at 11,749.25.
